title: Trish Kay
text: The car was in good condition but I was Quote: d $85 insurance then charged $112. Car was 2 door which was disappointing and confusion at Melbourne airport about where we had to go to pick up. Drop off was easy and the young man that took our keys was awesome. A couple of the Receiption staff could do with retraining on customer service. The girl who served us was alright but the girl working with her was abrupt.
